# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# SECRETS — never commit these.
# The ONLY env file that is committed is .env.production, and it may
# contain NEXT_PUBLIC_* values ONLY (those are compiled into the browser
# bundle and are public by design). Every real secret — ANTHROPIC_API_KEY,
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY, VAPID_PRIVATE_KEY, CRON_SECRET, Google client
# secret — lives in Vercel > Settings > Environment Variables. Nowhere else.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
.env.development
.env.test
*.pem
*.key

